= Mix_PlayMusic =

Play Music 

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
int Mix_PlayMusic(Mix_Music *music, int loops);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''music'''
|music
|-
|'''loops'''
|loops
|}

== Return Value ==

Returns which channel was used to play the music.

== Version ==

This function is available since SDL_mixer 2.0.0.

